Description:
LIGHT FILLED 2 BEDROOM/SOHO WITH A COMMANDING LOCATION
This light filled apartment/small office home office on the 4th floor of the Site One complex has plenty to offer. With an impressive location this apartment is situated opposite Etihad stadium, and only minutes walk away from tram stops, city circle and Southern Cross station. Easy access to freeways, Melbourne CBD, South Warf, Crown Casino, local shops, cafe and restaurants.
This fantastic residential apartment features:
- 2 spacious bedrooms
- Generous bathroom with access to laundry nook
- Low maintenance kitchen with stainless steel appliances
- Spacious open plan living and dining area
- Floor to ceiling windows beaming with natural light
- 1 Secure under cover car park
- Secure intercom access
- On site building manager
Potential rent of about
$500 per week, this fantastic opportunity will suite the savvy investor looking to add to their portfolio or owner occupier looking for a private get away city pad retreat.

Description:
5 CAR SPACES SOLD – 401 Docklands Drive, Aquavista Tower
5 CAR SPACES SOLD
Definitely perfect for private investor or owner occupier!
Aquavista Tower – entry from Doepel Way, Docklands VIC 3008
The Aquavista Tower is conveniently located directly across the entry to 14 Doepel Way, Docklands VIC 3008 (NewQuay) and is adjacent to Harbour Town Shopping Centre. Lots in this location are always in demand.
There are 7 car space available in prime harbour side location, perfectly positioned within the commercial precinct specifically developed for small business.
Lot Numbers: 450, 451, 458, 459, 460
Features:
• Lockable bollards to protect space
• Access via security swipe
• Undercover Parking
• Boom Gate installed at entry
• Towing facilities available for any breach of your parking space via anytime towing
• Direct access to citylink and all major Melbourne arterial roads
• Lift access from parking space to ground floor
Please note: a congestion levy of $1410 per year, per car space, applies to non-residential car park tenants (including businesses).
No congestion levy charged for any car park tenant residing in docklands

Description:
Modern Sophistication and Exceptional Outdoor Entertaining
With a stunning entertainer’s terrace that offers amazing space that will cater for those who love to enjoy alfresco meals and drinks all year round, this fabulous two bedroom, two bathroom apartment is a captivating offering in the classy Quays complex.
From the free-flowing floorplan to the undoubted quality and sleek style throughout, this apartment is a class above. We need to start with the impressive terrace which has more space than you’ll know what to do and is matched by charming views to the South and West. This large outdoor space has access from the open living and meals zone and the master bedroom which comes with a dazzling ensuite and built-in robes.
The kitchen showcases beautiful black cabinetry, glass splashback and stainless steel appliances, meanwhile the 2nd bedroom also with BIR has easy access to the designer bathroom with laundry and small study area near the entry. Other features include reverse cycle heating and cooling in the lounge and each beroom, secure intercom and car space.
Enjoy a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, while there is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge. Also make the most of a rooftop garden with BBQ, dining facilities and tennis court. Location wise, you can take advantage of the recently upgraded The District Docklands nearby, while you’re also close to promenade restaurants, Etihad Stadium and trams taking you across the city and beyond.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
STUNNING 2 BEDROOM IN THE NORTH OVERLOOKING POOL
A fantastic opportunity to secure this stunning and stylish 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment in the award winning Watergate Complex.
With a desirable location unmatched and packed with features and facilities, this spacious 2 bedroom will be at the top of your list.
Apartment 1204 at 18 at Waterview Walk is positioned on the 12th floor and facing the CBD. This spacious 2 bedroom residence has plenty to offer:
- Large & spacious main bedroom with floor to ceiling windows, small study nook and complete with built in mirrored wardrobes.
- Additional 2nd bedroom with floor to ceiling windows facing CBD.
- Generous open plan living and dining area and direct access to a stretched balcony with dual access from master bedroom and living area.
- White polish finished kitchen with plenty of cupboard storage including island bench/breakfast bar and large fridge space, SMEG stainless steel appliances including 4 burner gas cook top, range hood & dishwasher.
- Spacious bathroom with European laundry access
- Heating & Cooling.
- Secure intercom/video access.
- Secure basement parking
5 Star Facilities/Additional Features:
- Access to a very well equipped gym.
- Access to a heated pool with spa.
- Access to Sauna.
- Access to Entertainment area for guests and private functions.
Public Transport & Location:
- Free City Circle Tram at your door step.
- Short stroll to Melbourne CBD & Crown Casino.
- Within 5 minutes walk to Southern Cross Train Station & Etihad Stadium.
- Watergate is positioned between Collins St, Harbour Esp and Latrobe St tram stops.
- Walking distance to South Warf DFO.
- Close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre.
- Plenty of green parklands nearby and access to a public basketball court at the front of the building.
Property is currently leased at $530 per week making this also a very secure and sound investment. Property will be sold with all furnishings. Potential rental yield today $570-$600 per week.
With a rare and unique floor plan, access to 5 star facilities and positioned in a great location, this 2 bedroom apartment at Watergate Towers should be at the top of your shopping list.

Description:
Renovated Palladio Home with Views you will Never Forget
Modern and designer Docklands living has never looked as good as this stylish 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment, which also has the benefit of the most resplendent views which include Victoria Harbour, Marvel Stadium and the city.
With freshly laid timber flooring and carpet, this immaculate and stunningly presented 9th floor property in the Palladio complex is an exceptional opportunity for owner-occupiers looking for an upgrade or entry into the family friendly building. Elegant timber floors line the relaxed living and casual meals zones, with the pristine kitchen features inhabiting this central space and includes stainless steel appliances.
The large undercover balcony produces the astonishing views and is a charming alfresco area ideal to enjoy summer meals and drinks with friends and family. The master bedroom has a built-in robe and chic renovated ensuite, meanwhile the 2nd bedroom offers a BIR and its own small balcony. Further features include a renovated central bathroom, concealed laundry, split system heat/cool, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym and private function area.
Take advantage of this brilliant NewQuay precinct location which is close to an array of terrific restaurants including Oscars Table, Woolshed, Wok on the Dock and Berth. You’re also a short walk to The District Docklands, Marvel Stadium and trams in all directions.
To arrange an inspection, please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 or Lynn Lum on 0474 044 293.

The Merchant on Bourke
For sale is a superb 1 bedroom apartment in the cleverly designed Boutique residential complex in the Heart of the Docklands along Bourke Street.
A north facing apartment provides plenty of natural light. Great open plan layout providing plenty of space for the dining and living area which adjoins a balcony overlooking a landscaped garden.
Modern galley kitchen with glass splash back, stone benchtop and quality stainless steel appliances including Gas cook top. Plenty of storage.
Large dual access bedroom with built in mirrored robes. Stylish bathroom with twin access, incorporates laundry nook.
Other features include
• Reverse cycle split system air conditioner

• Tiled flooring in kitchen and bathroom.
• Security entrance
Close to Woolworths, The Library at the Dock and the wonderous cafes and eateries there for you to enjoy. Free tram zoned and just a short stroll to Southern Cross station.

888 Collins: Sophistication and space in abundance
Beautifully appointed and offering space rarely seen for an apartment of this type, this ultra-generous and stylish 1 bedroom + study 11th floor residence in the ’888 Collins’ complex represents an enticing prospect for owner-occupiers and those with investment aspirations.
From the high end quality to fabulous attention to detail, this modern pad is worth your time. Make the most of generous and open living and meals, undercover balcony with a westerly aspect, straight line stone kitchen with stainless steel Miele appliances, bedroom with mirrored built-in robe, sizeable study, elegant bathroom with rain shower, timber floors, European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, and secure car space.
Residents have access to amazing facilities as part of the ‘888 Collins’ building including a lap pool and spa, fully-equipped gymnasium, business lounge, podium garden with BBQ and putting green, sky garden with outstanding views, and access to the exclusive Club 888. You’re in close proximity to Buluk Park, Woolworths supermarket, local eateries including Squires Loft, Indi Hots, and Saluministi, Library at The Dock, Victoria Harbour promenade which great for long walks, and trams.

Description:
Marvellous Water Views
As the sun rises from the city skyline, what a beautiful backdrop to wake up to.
Position perfect, this 2 bedroom apartment in H1 on the 19th floor will provide the ideal home on the city fringe.
For those that enjoy cooking at home, one will notice the spacious kitchen with all the necessary stainless steel appliances including a gas stove and a large peninsula stone benchtop.
The open plan dining and living area adjoins the City facing balcony with glass balustrade capturing the glistening waters of the harbour. The perfect spot to sit back to either relax in the morning with a coffee and newspaper or winding down at the days end with a glass of wine absorbing the fairy lights of the city skyline and the shimmering colours reflecting off the marina.
Two bedrooms with mirrored BIR’s share the stylish tiled bathroom incorporating laundry.
With a uniform layout ensuring every use of space is maximised.
Features include
• Ducted heating and cooling
• Library
• Car park on title
• Storage Cage
• Gymnasium
Enjoy the eateries and cafés close by. Take a leisurely stroll along the promenade. Shop at the District Docklands. With the soon to be built Cinemas, Dan Murphy and Woolworths, there will be so much on offer.
Transport is a breeze with the Free City Zone Tram, Southern Cross Train Station and excellent Freeway system.
Ready to move in - call Eugene Louey on 0401 299 997 now to inspect!

Unique New York Loft Style Apartment in the Docklands

Description:
Bright Corner Apartment in the Exclusive NewQuay Precinct
Experience the best in striking modern living that also promises a wonderful corner position and sensational northerly views, this exceptional and pristine two bedroom apartment has an exclusive position in the Palladio complex.
NewQuay Precinct living has never looked as attractive as this easy care 18th floor retreat. Full floor-to-ceiling windows allows for amazing natural light through the relaxed lounge and meals zone, which offers a handy study nook while also promising access out to the north-facing balcony which takes in spectacular views.
The stylish kitchen includes stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher, meanwhile the bright main bedroom shares the brilliant northerly vistas and comes equipped with built-in robe storage. Other highlights include a 2nd bedroom or potential study, premium bathroom with European laundry, heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space and access to a health club with rooftop pool, gym and private function area.
You’ll love the summer months down on the waterfront where you can lap up the breezy lifestyle and enjoy fantastic restaurants which include Cargo, Docklands Pizzeria, Sir Basil and Woolshed. You’re also in close proximity to The District Docklands, IGA supermarket, Marvel Stadium and trams.

Description:
Under Instructions from the Mortgagee
A fantastic opportunity to secure a spacious sun filled and chic, North facing one-bedroom, balconied apartment in the renowned “The Quays” development. Beautifully appointed, this attractive apartment will suit out of towners looking for a town base, CBD professionals and first home owners alike or savvy investors. Situated only moments from the water and within an easy stroll of Harbour Town, Marvel Stadium and the Melbourne CBD, this terrific apartment is also advantaged by a secure car park on title. While a multitude of tram options can zip you wherever you’d like to go as well.
Comprising:
Secure
Entrance foyer
Spacious sunny living room with balcony access (air-conditioning)
Modern designer open plan kitchen
Large bedroom with mirrored built-in robes
Separate modern tiled bathroom with European laundry
The Quays offers a plethora of off lifestyle options to keep you fit, relaxed and entertaining your guests. The Health Club offers a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and yoga studio, while the Residents Club features library, boardroom for hire and business centre. A private dining room and cinema lounge. Further options include a rooftop garden with BBQ facilities.
All this lifestyle is packed into a brilliant location, where your backyard features Docklands District – Shopping Precinct, O’Brien Group Arena – Ice Skating, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel and an abundance of casual to fine dining eateries, bars and entertainment options.
Inspect as advertised or by appointment.
For further assistance please contact Matt Davidson on 0447 766 630 or Richard Crane on 0412 333 331.

Description:
Exquisite 36th floor new residence with 2 master bedrooms
Boasting a sky high position perched on the 36th floor of the magnificent Marina Tower, this brand new 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom corner residence is a contemporary superstar that offers 2 master bedrooms, 2 relaxed balconies, and 2 handy secure car spaces.
A unique apartment like this doesn’t come along very often. A long entry hall flows into the generous central living and dining zone with premium timber floors, where full windows act as a frame for you to enjoy east and south views including the city, bay, and Victoria Harbour in the distance. The dazzling kitchen impresses with premium stone, an island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances, while this casual central area has access out to a south-facing balcony with bay views which is ideal for summer dinners and drinks!
There is a 2nd balcony with CBD vistas as part of one of the master bedrooms, which further showcases built-in robe storage and a luxe ensuite. The 2nd master bedroom also has a BIR and ensuite with freestanding bath, meanwhile the sizeable 3rd bedroom shares the incredible city views. Other property features include a concealed laundry, split system heating and cooling, secure intercom, and the 2 car spaces.
Make the most of Marina Tower facilities which include lobby lounge, library, private business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck. Also lap up the NewQuay precinct lifestyle close to The District Docklands, delightful restaurants, Moonee Ponds Cree Trail for weekend bike rides, Marvel Stadium for those who love the footy, and the 35, 70, and 86 trams on Docklands Drive.
To book an inspection, please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 or Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556.

Description:
Iconic City Views on Yarra's Edge
This striking contemporary apartment employs stylish design principles, substantial proportions, quality appointments and elegant style with the city's skyline as a fabulous backdrop. Sun-bathed and generously proportioned, the living and dining domain is accompanied by a broad balcony with breathtaking views and a stone kitchen featuring stainless appliances and integrated fridge. Three inviting bedrooms, each enjoy Bay views, with the expansive master bedroom featuring a spa ensuite with double vanity. Additional features include favoured northern orientation, video intercom, powder room and access to the multi-level RekDek-gymnasium, glass edged pool, sauna and spa facilities. Privacy and security are at the forefront of this exceptional Tower apartment, while the added assets of basement parking for two vehicles and two storage boxes prove a perfect conclusion to this memorable property on the city's edge.

Description:
Spectacular Internal & External space with Stylish Conder Flair
Located in the highly sought-after ‘Conder’ building by renowned Melbourne architect Fender Kastalidis, and displaying awe-inspiring 270 degree views and marvelous internal and external space, this 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom apartment is a celebration of modern Docklands living.
Graced with stunning floor-to-ceiling windows, and an abundance of natural light, this 4th floor retreat is truly spectacular. With approximately 148m2 of internal space this property offers generous living and dining areas. This property also boasts approximately 71m2 of external space which, can be enjoyed form either two of the enormous terrace spaces, perfect for entertaining.
The superb Conder complex offers facilities including a pool, gym, and outdoor recreation area. You’re located in the excellent NewQuay precinct which allows residents to easily access terrific local eateries including The Waterside Oriental Bistro, NewQuay International Buffet, and The Conder restaurant. You’re further near Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco, Medibank Icehouse, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Festival Hall, and a tram stop at the door in the free tram zone! Great transport links with the 70 tram which takes you through the CBD, MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn, and Box Hill, the 75 tram to the popular Bridge Street Shops, the 86 through Bourke Street mall and trendy Brunswick, and a short walk or tram to Southern Cross Station and the Skybus to the airport.
The quality kitchen equipped with stainless steel benchtops and appliances plus a handy breakfast bar. All three bedrooms also own impeccable city views including the large master retreat which features an ensuite, while the central bathroom is brilliantly placed right next to the other bedrooms (with BIRs). All three bedrooms have access to one of the large terraces unique to the 4th level.
Other features of this apartment include a generous laundry with storage, central heat/cool, gas fireplace, double glazing throughout, video intercom, and 2 secure car spaces. Don’t miss out on this exceptional Conder opportunity!
Please contact Charles on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
Living at its finest!
Located on Pearl River Road, Docklands, Marina is Waterfront living at its finest and will redefine the way you view apartment living!
Apartment is featured with open-plan living and dining area with direct access to spacious balcony. More design highlights can be found in the kitchen, where luxury is the theme. Stone kitchen island with Miele appliances, split system heating and cooling and secure intercom. Generous bedroom with dual mirrored built-in robes and access to ensuite which comes with European laundry.
In a city famous for its great food and thriving café culture, residents will be spoilt for choice with a wide selection of places to eat, drink & entertain at your doorstep.
These stunning apartments have been architecturally designed and sit right in the heart of Docklands, on the fringe of Melbourne's CBD. This location enjoys access to a variety of public amenities; in particular, Harbour Town Shopping District, Harbour Ferry, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Direct Factory Outlet, City Circle Tram, Capital City Bicycle Trail, a short stroll to Southern Cross Station and only a short tram ride to RMIT University, the University of Melbourne, the State Library and Bourke Street Mall, as well as a myriad of bars, restaurants and cafes.
Marina is positioned on Victoria Harbour, overlooking Melbourne's skyline and the ever-changing marina. This complex offers a tranquil escape from the nearby bustling city.
Residents and their guests will enjoy a thoughtful array of tailored facilities including;
Features:
International waterfront address
Architecturally designed apartments
Fully equipped Gymnasium & 25m Lap Pool located on Level 7
Library, Gallery Space, Business Centre & Conference Rooms
Private Cinema and Billiard Room
Private Dining & Kitchen
Ground-floor hotel restaurant and cafe
Call today to register your interest!

Description:
UNDER OFFER - Victoria Harbour Living with Scenic Park & Skyline Views
Boasting a wonderful easterly orientation which allows for beautiful Docklands Park views with Etihad Stadium and other buildings also in the distance, this smart and spacious two bedroom apartment offers a peace and tranquility that is so hard to find in living this close to the city.
The sensational central lounge and meals zone is defined by its open and sizeable layout, with the undercover balcony accessed via sliding doors from the main area and displays gorgeous tree views that will have a truly calming effect. The stone kitchen is also included in the lounge/meals hub and delivers stone surfaces, island bench and stainless steel appliances including a dishwasher. The property has just been painted and carpeted throughout.
The bedrooms feature fabulous privacy separated by the sleek bathroom and both come with built-in robe storage. Other property features include a concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, video intercom, storage cage and secure car space.
Access a scenic community garden right next door, while you’re also close to The Hub @ Docklands, cafes and restaurants including Caffe Bambino, Cafenatics, The Merchant Society, and Banoi Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Docklands Park, Capital City Trail, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
To arrange an exclusive viewing please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304.
